title: WHO has not seen any reports of deaths caused by omicron variant, urges people not to panic as delta still dominant
content:
1. WHO has not seen any reports of deaths caused by omicron variant, urges people not to panic as delta still dominant  MarketWatch
  2. WHO says Covid omicron variant detected in 38 countries, early data suggests it's more contagious than delta  CNBC
  3. Spreading rapidly in Europe, Omicron variant sparks a wave of new restrictions  Yahoo News
  4. Vaccine makers right to plan for adjustments to COVID-19 shot, says WHO  Reuters
  5. Africa alerted the world to Omicron. Why are we now the pariahs?  The Guardian
